{
  "stem": "2735.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And we were running the way we were.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "That's what we had on us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Meanwhile, the woman started to deliver a baby.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And-- and-- no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We met them-- oh, in Kharkiv.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I have to tell you about Kharkiv.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Before we came to Kharkiv, they mobilized us to take down the crop from the fields, because the Germans are closing in and they don't want to leave any food for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And we have to feed the army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And that it's your patriotic duty to-- to work on the fields.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So going there, we stop in a town, a small town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we see a bunch of students-- girls-- that they took from the Kharkiv University to take down the-- to do the same job.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we stayed the day there, and we got very close with the girls.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when we said goodbye, we didn't know where they're taking us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They said, remember, this is the address.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see where we live.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you get-- they didn't know what we're going to do or nothing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When you can-- I don't remember exactly-- but we promised that we'll see them again.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They took us to a place-- a-- a barn.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A lot of people were there with a lot of-- with straw.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't remember if the animals were there or the animals were removed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they told us, gave us that patriotic speech that we have to help.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was very patriotic-- I mean, that we have to remove from the fields everything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My middle sister, that one that's a nurse, she had a habit that she needed a nap in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they took us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "First, we've never been to a field.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I didn't know what are potatoes and what are weeds.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
